    "Your least developed function — Introverted Intuition — handles abstract pattern recognition and long-range meaning-making. Under stress, it can produce sudden, vivid pessimistic visions of the future that feel prophetically certain but are actually anxiety in disguise. In healthy development, it gives you moments of genuine strategic insight that complement your tactical excellence.",
